      <h2>3. Strengths</h2>
      <ul class="features">
        <li><strong>Powerful Search & Filters:</strong> Helps find restaurants quickly.</li>
        <li><strong>Visual Menus:</strong> Photos and reviews build trust.</li>
        <li><strong>Live Tracking:</strong> Real-time order updates reduce anxiety.</li>
        <li><strong>Personalization:</strong> Relevant recommendations based on history.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Weaknesses</h2>
        <ul class="features">
          <li><strong>Cluttered Home Screen:</strong> Many banners and promos reduce discoverability.</li>
          <li><strong>Complex Checkout Flow:</strong> Manual coupon selection and address edits cause friction.</li>
          <li><strong>Notification Noise:</strong> Frequent irrelevant promotions disturb users.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

